642
00:35:24,530 --> 00:35:25,490
I do mean it.

643
00:35:25,970 --> 00:35:27,010
You should kill me.

644
00:35:27,700 --> 00:35:28,970
You know I'm a traitor.

645
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:31,130
