693
00:38:43,380 --> 00:38:44,300
I will pave

694
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:47,900
the way for you.

695
00:38:49,490 --> 00:38:50,660
You don't have to tell me

696
00:38:50,700 --> 00:38:51,530
