697
00:38:51,570 --> 00:38:53,260
I have no intention of
hearing it from you.

698
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:54,660
I already have my guesses.

699
00:39:14,120 --> 00:39:17,450
Dying is easy,

700
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,090
but you deserve

701
00:39:21,340 --> 00:39:22,840
